    Methods in com.tectonica.jonix.onix2 that return types with arguments of type Languages
    Modifier and Type
    Method
    Description
    ListOfOnixCodelist<LanguageCode,Languages>
    Contributor.languageCodes()
    Used only when the <ContributorRole> code value is B06, B08 or B10 indicating a translator, to specify the language from which the translation was made.
    ListOfOnixCodelist<LanguageOfText,Languages>
    Product.languageOfTexts()
    A code indicating a language in which the text of the product is written: optional, and repeatable if the text is in two or more languages.
